text: Arnaud Clément and Sébastien Grosjean were the defending champions but did not compete that year. Michael Hill and Jeff Tarango won in the final 7-6(7-2), 6-3 against Pablo Albano and David Macpherson. ==Seeds== # Michael Hill / Jeff Tarango (Champions) # Pablo Albano / David Macpherson (Final) # Julien Boutter / Daniel Orsanic (First Round) # Simon Aspelin / Johan Landsberg (First Round) ==Draw== ==External links== * 2001 Grand Prix Hassan II Doubles Draw Doubles \- Doubles, 2001 Grand Prix Hassan Ii
